etty confident this is the final release-candidate before launch, so please update your existing installations an [&hellip;]''>bbPress: bbPress 2.0 RC 5</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://blog.akismet.com/2011/09/12/vikings-viagra-and-versace-a-brief-history-of-spam/'' title=''The biggest gathering of WordPress users and developers takes place each year at WordCamp San Francisco. At this year’s three-day event, I gave a short presentation on the history of spam. Here’s the video: [&hellip;]''>Akismet: Vikings, Viagra, and Versace: A Brief History of Spam</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
